content: The end is in sight, many of my coworkers and I are getting our first doses of the #PfizerBioNTech #CovidVaccine today. But as Dr. Milani at @OchsnerHealth emphasizes, stay #vigilant, #MaskUp, do your part and protect your community. #Covid_19 We can end this!
date: 9:56 PM · Dec 14, 2020 from New Orleans, LA·Twitter for iPhone
